    "data": {
      "merge": "<ul><li><p>You have Resistance to fire damage.</p></li><li><p>Any fire damage you deal ignores Resistances.</p></li></ul>",
      "dismiss": "<p>When you dismiss this Arcanum, choose Forge or Inferno:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Forge.</strong> You create a basic armor, shield, or weapon of your choice (see <strong>Core Rulebook,</strong> pages <strong>130</strong> to<strong> 133</strong>). If you select this option again, the previously created item vanishes. If you create a weapon this way, it deals fire damage instead of physical.</p></li><li><p><strong>Inferno.</strong> Choose any number of creatures you can see: each of them <strong>suffers</strong> <strong>30 fire damage. </strong>This damage <strong>ignores Resistances.</strong></p><hr></li></ul><ul><li><p><strong>Targets</strong>: @DMG[30 fire|ignore-resistances|]{Inferno}</p></li></ul>",
